        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{ ({\n  contents: [\n    {\n      parts: [\n        {\n          text: `You are a senior B2B growth strategist for [Your Company Name].\n\n[Your Company Name] is not an agency. It is an embedded growth and marketing pod for ambitious startups and growth-stage companies. [Your Company Name] works inside the client's workflows/OKRs like an internal growth team and owns execution across paid acquisition, SEO, content, lifecycle/email, social, positioning, automation, and GTM systems.\n\nPosition [Your Company Name] as: the growth co-founder/team the company has not hired yet — fast, embedded, execution-led, and cheaper than building a full in-house team.\n\nCompany Name:\n${$('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Company Name']}\n\nWebsite:\n${$('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Website']}\n\nFirst Name:\n${$('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['First Name'] || 'Not provided'}\n\nTitle:\n${$('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Title'] || 'Not provided'}\n\nManual ICP:\n${$('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['ICP'] || 'Not provided'}\n\nMarket Signal:\n${$('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Market Signal'] || 'Not provided'}\n\nWebsite Research:\n${$('Clean Website Text').item.json['website_text'] || 'Not provided'}\n\nSocial Links:\n${$('Prepare Social Links').item.json['social_links'] || 'Not provided'}\n\nAnalyze the company and infer:\n- ICP\n- company summary\n- likely pain points\n- where [Your Company Name] can help\n\nOutreach rules:\n- Use First Name if available.\n- Tailor to Title if available.\n- Use Market Signal naturally only if relevant.\n- Reference at most ONE specific observation.\n- Keep email concise, human, operator-to-operator, non-salesy.\n- Avoid buzzwords, fake names, placeholders, and generic agency language.\n- Position [Your Company Name] as an embedded growth pod, not an agency.\n- End with a soft CTA for a brief 15-minute conversation next week.\n- End exactly with:\n\nBest,\n[Your Company] Growth Division\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON:\n{\n  \"generated_icp\": \"Ideal customer profile inferred from research\",\n  \"company_summary\": \"3-5 line summary based on research\",\n  \"pain_points\": \"Specific likely pain points inferred from research\",\n  \"outreach_draft\": \"Personalized outreach email\"\n}\n`\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}) }}",
        "options": {
          "batching": {
            "batch": {
              "batchSize": 1,
              "batchInterval": 10000
            }
          }
        }
      },
